{
  "stem": "3820.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I remember there were certain times when I was forbidden to go out of the house, or to go play with someone.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- periodically, German-- the motorcycle with the sidecar and a truck full of Germans would drive through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- then the children were being-- would be kept inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was fear, and we could feel it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we never knew from day to day what was happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I think people's tempers were short.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there were no goodies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I know I didn't remember what any-- what any certain foods looked like.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very, very-- there was hunger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- we-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I just remember that the family stayed a lot together as much as they could, in whatever manner, in-- in the house.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We-- As I said, my grandfather's business was the leather, the shoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were forced to make the shoes for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So every now and then, they would come to the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I'd-- all I remember is that there's-- even to this day, there seemed to be such an-- such an arrogance in-- in the stance of the-- of the-- of the men, the German men that came.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As if no one counted, and-- flies on a wall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I guess I was one of the lucky ones, because I didn't live in the ghetto very long.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we all had to have the star on our clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there wasn't much clothing-- whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no way to purchase anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no way to make anything, whether it was material.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever we had, we made do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As children grew, we-- we gave to-- to the littler ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
